OL,3,CChanges introduced on 14th June
OL,4,C
OL,5,FThere have been a number of changes to
OL,6,FtheGTV GuideFsection onGP200.
OL,8,GBBC ScotlandFandGS4CFare available for
OL,9,Fthe first time, as are UKTV'sGU&Dave,
OL,10, U&Drama, U&EdenFandGU&Yesterday.
OL,12,FIrish channels fromGRTE, TG 4Fand
OL,13,GVirgin MediaFhave also been added.
OL,15,FThere's also now almost full coverage
OL,16,FofGBBC OneFandGITV 1Fregions. The full
OL,17,Fguide for that is onGP260.
OL,19,FTo accommodate some of the changes to
OL,20,Fthe TV section, we've had to move the
OL,21,Fvarious regional news indices. The new
OL,22,Fpage numbers are listed onGP301.
